{
  "stem": "18258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 242.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was my only impression.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Otherwise, I liked Budapest very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a nice city, second to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I wrote at that time it's certainly a very non-Aryan people, the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there, the Nazis were already making their inroad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In Vienna, all over the streets were illegal, tolerated swastikas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People were marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had official gatherings, assemblies in the various halls in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It just-- they were not suppressed anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Immediately after the Anschluss, they came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And within-- it was on a Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were in our store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we-- that Friday afternoon, we were supposed to prepare for the plebiscite.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sunday was supposed to be the plebiscite for Anschluss to Germany or for independence of Austria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was Schuschnigg's last act before he went to Berchtesgaden and was convinced.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we had-- as store owners, we had been given official posters to put in our windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Vote for independence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Until-- and from the, the unions, from the outlying districts, they marched into the street-- or demonstrating for independence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then came the radio announcement that Schuschnigg had capitulated, had ordered the Austrian Army not to resist the German invasion, to avoid bloodshed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the same masses of people who had marched into the inner city in the afternoon, three hours laters, marched back to their outlying district already with swastika armbands and yelling the Sieg Heil, and, 'We love our Fuhrer,' and 'Down with the Jews,' 'Kill the Jews.' And we quickly took those posters out of our windows.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we knew it had-- hell had started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And next morning when we went down, opened our store, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the police already had swastika armbands.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
